title: Santa's Workshop Coloring Book
description:
A visit behind the scenes of Santa's amazing workshop. Enjoy 40 pages of illustrations to color, in which humor and details float through the different floors of the workshop. It's the ideal activity to wait until Santa Claus arrives!
  • Format: Softcover
  • Dimensions: 8.26 x 11.7 in.
  • Materials: Paper and cardboard from sustainably managed forests, and natural inks
  • Ages 3 and up
